**Tests:** ⚠️ The `tests:` frontmatter field points to `scripts/generate-mapping.sh` — a utility script, not an actual test. No unit/integration tests were written. CLAUDE.md specifies the workflow as spec → failing tests → implement. Verification was purely manual (`tsc --noEmit`, `next build`). For an F-000 scaffold this is borderline acceptable, but spec status `implemented` with all acceptance criteria checkboxes unchecked (`[ ]`) is inconsistent.

