### 3. Integration Quality

**Issues found:**

- **`lib/db/duckdb.ts:10`** — `process.env.HOME ?? "/Users/brianfischman"` — hardcoded username path as fallback. Non-portable; only works on one machine. This was subsequently fixed in commit `a6372d74`.
- **`components/DeckFilterBar.tsx`** — Component uses local `useState` but never reads from or writes to `useDeckStore`. The Zustand store exists (`lib/store/deck.ts`) with the exact matching filter fields, but the two are disconnected.
