```typescript
const colorMap: Record<string, string> = {};
if (statsQuery.data) { ... }
// Used in useEffect deps: [mapReady, pointsQuery.data, colorMap]
```
`colorMap` is a new object literal every render. The `useEffect` depending on it will re-run continuously after data loads. Should be `useMemo`.

