**Drift**: Spec frontmatter declares `tests: - tests/widgets/recent-transactions.test.ts` but the actual file is at `tests/db/recent-transactions.test.ts`. This is a spec↔code mismatch in the frontmatter.

**UI gap**: The ASCII mockup includes a `[ Load more ]` button and pagination behavior; the implementation has no pagination — it fetches up to 50 records with a count footer only.

**Property type filter gap**: `PROPERTY_TYPES` constant is defined and wired into the DB/tRPC layer but the UI renders no property type filter control.

