### Framework Compliance

| Check | Result |
|---|---|
| Feature spec created with YAML frontmatter | ✅ All required fields present |
| Gherkin scenarios | ✅ 8 scenarios — happy path, filtering, inheritance, empty/loading states |
| ASCII mockup | ✅ |
